{"kanda":6,"sarga":113,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"रावणंनिहतंदृष्टवाराघवेणमहात्मना ।अन्तःपुराद्विनिष्पेतूराक्षस्यश्शोककर्शिताः","trans":"On seeing Ravana killed by the great soul Raghava, the Rakshasas from the gynaeceum stricken with grief rushed out.","words":[{"d":"महात्मना","m":"great soul"},{"d":"राघवेण","m":"by Raghava"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"निहतम्","m":"killed"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"राक्षस्यः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"शोककर्शिताः","m":"stricken with grief"},{"d":"अन्तःपुरात्","m":"from the gynaeceum"},{"d":"विनिष्पेतुः","m":"rushed out"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"वार्यमाणास्सुबहुशोवेष्टन्त्यःक्षितिपांसुषु ।विमुक्तकेश्यश्शोकार्तागावोवत्सहतायथा","trans":"Numerous women, though obstructed, were rolling in dust, with dishevelled hair and crying like cows which had lost their calves.","words":[{"d":"सुबहुशो:","m":"numerous Rakshasa women"},{"d":"वार्यमाणाः","m":"obstructed"},{"d":"क्षितिपांसुषु","m":"rolling in dust"},{"d":"वेष्ट्नत्यः","m":"encompassing"},{"d":"विमुक्तकेश्यः","m":"dishevelled"},{"d":"वत्सहताः","m":"young ones lost"},{"d":"गावःयथा","m":"like cows"},{"d":"शोकार्ताः","m":"crying"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"उत्तरेणविनिष्क्रम्यद्वारेणसहराक्षसैः ।प्रविश्यायोधनंघोरंविचिन्वन्त्वोहतंपतिम् आर्यपुत्रेतिवादिन्योहानाथेति च सर्वशः ।परिपेतुःकबन्धाङ्कांमहींशोणितकर्दमाम्","trans":"The Rakshasa women along with Rakshasas came out of the north gate and entered the battlefield screaming 'O son', 'O husband' and crying, seeing the trunks soaked in blood and mud on the ground and went about all over.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसैःसह","m":"along with Rakshasas"},{"d":"उत्तरेणद्वारेण","m":"northern gate"},{"d":"विनिष्क्रम्य","m":"coming out"},{"d":"हतम्","m":"killed"},{"d":"पतिम्","m":"husbands"},{"d":"विचिन्वन्त्वः","m":"crying"},{"d":"घोरम्","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"अयोधनम्","m":"battlefield"},{"d":"प्रविश्य","m":"entered"},{"d":"आर्यपुत्रेति","m":"O son"},{"d":"हानाथेति","m":"ha husband"},{"d":"वादिन्यः","m":"speaking"},{"d":"कबन्धाङ्काम्","m":"trunks"},{"d"