":"full of splendor"},{"d":"नीलाञ्जनचयोपमम्","m":"like heap of dark mountain"},{"d":"निहतम्","m":"killed"},{"d":"भूमौ","m":"on the ground"},{"d":"ददृशुः","m":"looked"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"ताःपतिंसहसादृष्टवाशयानंरणपांसुषु ।निपेतुस्तस्यगात्रेषुछिन्नावनलताइव","trans":"In the battlefield they saw their husband lying, and precipitately fell on his limbs like broken creepers in a garden.","words":[{"d":"ताः","m":"they"},{"d":"रणपांसुषु","m":"in the battlefield"},{"d":"शयानम्","m":"lying"},{"d":"पतिम्","m":"husband"},{"d":"सहसा","m":"precipitately"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"छिन्नाः","m":"broken"},{"d":"वनलताइव","m":"like creepers in a garden"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"गात्रेषु","m":"limbs"},{"d":"निपेतुः","m":"fallen"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"बहुमानात्परिष्वज्यकाचिदेवंरुरोद ह ।चरणौकाचिदालम्ब्यकाचित्कण्ठेऽवलम्ब्य च","trans":"Indeed, out of respect some embraced him and roared aloud, some held his feet and wept, some held his neck and started weeping.","words":[{"d":"काचित्","m":"indeed"},{"d":"बहुमानात्","m":"out of great respect"},{"d":"एनम्","m":"they"},{"d":"परिष्वज्य","m":"embracing"},{"d":"रुरोद ह","m":"roared aloud"},{"d":"काचित्","m":"some"},{"d":"चरणौ","m":"feet"},{"d":"आलम्ब्य","m":"holding"},{"d":"काचित्","m":"some"},{"d":"कण्ठे","m":"neck"},{"d":"अवलम्ब्य च","m":"started weeping"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"उत्क्षिप्य च भुजौकाचिद्भूमौसुपरिवर्तते ।हतस्यवदनंदृष्टवाकाचिन्मोहमुपागमत्","trans":"Some lifting their arms threw themselves on ground, some rolled, some beholding the dead Ravana's face became deluded.","words":[{"d":"काचित्","m":"some"},{"d":"भुजौ","m":"arms"},{"d":"उत्क्षिप्य","m":"throwing herself on ground"},{"d":"भूमौ","m":"on ground"},{"d":"सुपरिवर्तते","m":"rolled"},{"d":"काचित्","m":"some"},{"d":"हतस्य","m":"killed"},{"d":"वदनम्","m":"face"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"मोहम्","m":"in delusion"},{"d":"उपागमत्","m":"holding"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"काचिदङ्केशिरःकृत्वारुरोदमुखमीक्षती ।स्नापयन्तीमुखंबाष्पैस्तुषारैरिवपङ्कजम्","trans":"One held his head on her lap, and one held his face and looking at it shed tears, like nature covers lotus with dew and roared.","words":[{"d":"काचित्","m":"some"},{"d":"शिरः","m":"head"},{"d":"अङ्के","m":"lap"},{"d":"कृत्वा","m":"holding"},{"d":"मुखम्","m":"face"},{"d":"ईक्षती","m":"looking"},{"d":"तुषारैः","m":"nature sheds dew"},{"d":"पङ्कजम् इव","m":"like from lotus"},{"d":"मुखम्","m":"face"},{"d":"बाष्पैः","m":"tears"},{"d":"स्नापयन्ती","m":"flowed"},{"d":"रुरोद","m":"roared"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"एवमार्ताःपतिंदृष्टवारावणंनिहतंभुवि ।चुक्रुशुर्भहुधाशोकाद्भूयस्ताःपर्यदेवयन्","trans":"Afflicted on beholding their husband Ravana, killed, and lying on the ground, the Rakshasa women again and again cried exceedingly in many ways overcome with grief.","words":[{"d":"भुवि","m":"on the ground"},{"d":"निहतम्","m":"killed"},{"d":"पतिम्","m":"husband"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"beholding"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that manner"},{"d":"आर्ताः","m":"afflicted"},{"d":"ताः","m":"they"},{"d":"बहुधा","m":"many"},{"d":"चुक्रुशुः","m":"again and again"},{"d":"शोकात्","m":"in sorrow"},{"d":"भूयः","m":"exceedingly"},{"d":"पर्यदेवयन्","m":"overcome with grief"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"येनमित्रासितःशक्रोयेनवित्रासितोयमः ।येनवैश्रवणोराजापुष्पकेणवियोजितः गन्धर्वाणामृषीणां च सुराणां च महात्मनाम् ।भयंयेनरणेदत्तंसोऽयंशेतेरणेहतः","trans":"\"By whom Indra feared, by whom Yama feared, at whom king Visrava feared, by whom Pushpaka was deprived to Kubera in war, by whom Gandharvas and ascetics were afraid of, by whom high souled Suras were afraid of lies in the battlefield asleep.\"","words":[{"d":"येन","m":"to whom"},{"d":"शक्रः","m":"Indra"},{"d":"वित्रासितः","m":"feared"},{"d":"येन","m":"to whom"},{"d":"यमः","m":"Yama"},{"d":"वित्रासितः","m":"feared"},{"d":"येन","m":"to whom"},{"d":"राजा","m":"king"},{"d":"वैश्रवणः","m":"Visrava"},{"d":"पुष्पकेण्","m":"Pushpaka"},{"d":"वियोजितः","m":"used by winning"},{"d":"येन","m":"to whom"},{"d":"रणे","m":"in war"},{"d":"गन्धर्वाणाम्","m":"Gandharvas"},{"d":"ऋषीणां च","m":"and a