shasas could not kill, lies asleep, killed by a mortal who came by walk.\"","words":[{"d":"यः","m":"he who"},{"d":"देवतानाम्","m":"Devatas"},{"d":"तथा","m":"so also"},{"d":"दानवरक्षनाम्","m":"Danavas, Rakshasas"},{"d":"अवध्यः","m":"not be killed"},{"d":"सःअयम्","m":"he"},{"d":"पदातिना","m":"by walk"},{"d":"मानुषेण","m":"by a mortal"},{"d":"रणे","m":"in battle"},{"d":"हतः","m":"killed"},{"d":"शेते","m":"lies asleep"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"यो न शक्यस्सुरैर्हन्तुं न यक्षैर्नासुरैस्तथा ।सोऽयंकश्चिदिवासत्त्वोमृत्युंमर्त्येनलम्भितः","trans":"\"He, who could not be killed by Suras, Asuras or Yakshas, such a hero lies like a weak person devoid of strength, killed by a mortal, is resting.\"","words":[{"d":"यः","m":"he who"},{"d":"सुरैः","m":"Suras"},{"d":"हन्तुम्","m":"to kill"},{"d":"न शक्यः","m":"not possible"},{"d":"यक्षै:","m":"Yaksha"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"तथा","m":"so also"},{"d":"असुरैः","m":"Asuras"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"असत्त्वः","m":"weak"},{"d":"कश्चिदिव","m":"like one devoid of strength"},{"d":"मर्त्येन","m":"by death"},{"d":"मृत्युम्","m":"death"},{"d":"लम्भितः","m":"resting"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"एवंवदन्त्योरुरुदुस्तस्यतादुःखिताःस्त्रियः ।भूयएव च दुःखार्ताविलेपुश्चपुनःपुनः","trans":"Those women grieving in that way roared aloud, lamenting again and again cried, afflicted by sorrow.","words":[{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"दुःखिताः","m":"grieving"},{"d":"ताःस्त्रियःएवम्","m":"those women in that way"},{"d":"वदन्त्य:","m":"roaring"},{"d":"रुरुदुः","m":"aloud"},{"d":"भूयःएव च","m":"lamented again"},{"d":"दुःखार्ताः","m":"afflicted with sorrow"},{"d":"पुनःपुनः","m":"again and again"},{"d":"विलेपुः","m":"cried"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"अशृण्वतातुसुहृदांसततंहितवादिनाम् ।मरणायहृतासीताराक्षसाश्चनिपातिताः एतास्सममिदानींतेवयमात्मा च पातितः ।","trans":"\"You did not listen to the good advice of your dear and good at heart. You brought Sita and destroyed yourself and all of us at a time.\"","words":[{"d":"सततम्","m":"always"},{"d":"हितवादिनाम्","m":"your welfare"},{"d":"सुहृदाम्","m":"dear and good at heart"},{"d":"अश्वण्वता","m":"not listened"},{"d":"मरणाय","m":"death"},{"d":"सीता","m":"Sita"},{"d":"आहृता","m":"brought"},{"d":"राक्षसाश्च","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"निपातिताः","m":"struck down"},{"d":"आत्मा च","m":"yourself"},{"d":"पातितः","m":"destroyed"},{"d":"समम्","m":"at a time"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"एताःवयम्","m":"all of us"},{"d":"इदानीम्","m":"this way"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"ब्रुवाणोऽपिहितंवाक्यमिष्टोभ्राताविभीषणः धृष्टंपरुषितोमोहत्त्वयात्मवथकाङ्क्षिणा ।","trans":"\"Even though good advice was given by your dear brother Vibheeshana, in your delusion evidently you sought your own destruction.\"","words":[{"d":"हितम्","m":"good"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"ब्रुवाणोऽपि","m":"even though told"},{"d":"इष्टःभ्राता","m":"dear brother"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"धृष्टम्","m":"evidently"},{"d":"आत्मवथकाङ्णा","m":"sought your own destruction"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"by you"},{"d":"मोहात्","m":"in delusion"},{"d":"परुषितः","m":"harshly"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"दिनिर्यातितातेस्वासतीतारामायमैथिली ननस्स्याद्व्यसनंघोरमिदंमूलहरंमहत् ।","trans":"\"If Sita, princess of Mithila had been returned by you, this great destruction of the very root and calamity with you and for us would not have happened.\"","words":[{"d":"मैतिली","m":"Mythili"},{"d":"सीता","m":"Sita"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"रामाय","m":"Rama's"},{"d":"निर्यातिता","m":"returned"},{"d":"यदिस्यात्","m":"if so with you"},{"d":"नः","m":"not"},{"d":"मूलहरम्","m":"destruction of the very root"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"this"},{"d":"महत्","m":"great"},{"d":"घोरम्","m":"terrific"},{"d":"व्यसनम्","m":"calamity"},{"d":"न स्यात्","m":"not happened"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"वृत्तकामोभवेद्भ्रातारामोमित्रकुलंभवेत् वयंचाध्विवाःसर्वाःसकमा न च शत्रवः ।","trans":"\"If your brother's desire had been fulfilled Rama would have turned to be our friend. We would not have been widows. Our enemy's desire would not have been fulfilled.\"","words":[{"d":"न्राता","m":"brother"},{"d":"वृत्तकामः","m":"desire fulfilled"},{"d":"भवेत्","m":"would be"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"मित्रकुलम्","m":"turned to be friend"},{"d":"भवेत्","m":"would have been"},{"d":"वयम्","m":"our"},{"d":"सर्वाः","m":"all"},{"d":"अध्विनाः","m":"not widows"},{"d":"शत्रवः च","m":"enemy's"},{"d":"सकामाः","m":"that desire"},{"d":"न","m":"not"}]},{"v":22,"dev":"त्वयापुनर्नृशंशंसेनसीतांसंरुन्धताबलात् राक्षसावयमात्मा च त्रयंतुल्यंनिपातितम् ।","trans":"\"With evil intention you kept Sita under detention. These Rakshasas and you and us all the three are together destroyed.\"","words":[{"d":"नृशंसेन","m":"with evil intention"},{"d":"सीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"बलात्","m":"forcibly"},{"d":"संरुन्धता","m":"kept under detention"},{"d":"त्वयापुनः","m":"again by you"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"वयम्","m":"these आत्मा च and you too"},{"d":"त्रयम्","m":"three"},{"d":"तुल्यम्","m":"together"},{"d":"निपातितम्","m":"destroyed"}]},{"v":23,"dev":"न कामकारःकामंवातवराक्षसपुङ्गव ।दैवंचेष्टयतेसर्वंहतंदैवेनहन्यते","trans":"\"O Foremost of Rakshasas! You have acted according to your desire alone is not sufficient as divine will make you do everything. He is killed whom destiny kills.\"","words":[{"d":"राक्षसपुङ्गवः","m":"foremost of Rakshasas"},{"d":"कामम्","m":"desire"},{"d":"तव","m":"of yours"},{"d":"कामकारः","m":"acting to your will"},{"d":"न वा","m":"by you"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"all"},{"d":"दैवम्","m":"divine"},{"d":"चेष्टयते","m":"makes you do"},{"d":"देवेन","m":"by divine"},{"d":"हतम्","m":"killed"},{"d":"हन्यते","m":"kills"}]},{"v":24,"dev":"वानराणांविनाशोऽयंराक्षसानां च तेरणे ।तवचैवमहाबाहो दैवयोगादुपागतः","trans":"\"O mighty armed Ravana! For Vanaras, Rakshasas and you too, this destruction in this war has come by divine grace.\"","words":[{"d":"महाबाहो","m":"mighty armed"},{"d":"रणे","m":"in war"},{"d":"वानराणाम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"राक्षसानां च","m":"Rakshasas also"},{"d":"तव च","m":"you too"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"विनाशः","m":"destruction"},{"d":"दैवयोगात्","m"